title: Million Dollar Listing New York S03E09 I Dream Of Jeanne WEB-DL
description:
Ep 9: I Dream of Jeanne
Fredrik and Luis attempt to work together, while Ryan focuses on making a Michael Bay-style trailer for his listing.

Now that construction at the Sky Garage is progressing, it's time for Ryan to shoot his Michael Bay-style trailer for the most important listing of his career. . .the only question is: will it be a blockbuster or a box office flop? Meanwhile, outside of Manhattan, Fredrik represents a new developer in Brooklyn, who has multiple projects in the works. But when Luis agrees to meet the developer with Fredrik for a possible team-up in the future, the two agents prove, once and for all, that they don't play well together.
